725283f-b.title: Queens: 38th Street - 19th Avenue
725283f-b.text:
38th Street, south from 19th Avenue. The lumber piles
belong, In all likelihood, to the Steinway piano works
which are located in back of where the photographer stood.
P. L. Sperr
